{
  "stem": "20710.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But then the guy who was supervising the, the labor on this farm there, with, you know, with all these things that we took care of-- so he felt very bad for me because he felt that I worked so hard, you know, just the summer before.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And now I came back, and I, and I was sick, and couldn't walk, and this.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he said, now, [INAUDIBLE] we'll get you in, and he was Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was the one that this Lagerfuhrer lived in his house, because he had a very nice house like a villa.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he lived a there, and this, this Ukrainian who was supervising the work day on the fields, he lived, like, in one room, and he had a big basement.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he kept quite a few of us in the basement.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he said, we'll see.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They have to take you in, back to the-- it's a-- it's one-- it's a part of the, of the concentration camp, because he kept us like, you know, that nobody would know, because he wasn't allowed to.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nozarki, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were about six, and he kept us in the basement there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we did some work, and-- and then in the same time, they changed Lagerfuhrers, you know, because the summer before was [INAUDIBLE], and then they, they took him away, and they brought another one.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this other one, Kemke was his name, was supposed to be a much-- you know, a little bit, you know, less aggressive.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The other [INAUDIBLE] was very, very aggressive and very strict.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he said, we'll wait and see.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We have to get you back into camp, to the concentration camps of [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In the meanwhile, I came down with typhus fever.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
